# Tests that a graph can be created, three nodes and
# three edges from the same parent to the same child 
# and one edge from the same parent to a different child can be added, 
# and three nodes and four edges can be printed out.

# Create a graph
CreateGraph TheLordOfTheRing3

# Add three nodes
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing3 Frodo
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing3 Gandalf
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing3 Samwise

# Add four edges
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing3 Frodo Gandalf TheHobbit
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing3 Frodo Samwise TheReturnOfTheKing
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing3 Frodo Samwise TheTwoTowers
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing3 Frodo Samwise TheFellowshipOfTheRing

# Print the nodes in the graph and the outgoing edges from Frodo
ListNodes TheLordOfTheRing3
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing3 Frodo